    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, there's nobody \"who truly knows me\" here. i've spent years building this life and it feels so hollow. it's not even about being sad anymore, it's just this logical realization that my absence wouldn't change a single thing for anyone. it feels like i'm just a background character in everyone else's life, just... waiting to be edited out.",
