      "content": "it just feels so much more peaceful to think about it that way. like, if i'm just an extra in this movie, then disappearing wouldn't even be a plot hole. it would just be a quiet, clean exit. why is it considered \"wrong\" to just want to stop being a burden on a world i'm not even really part of?",
